        <p begin="00:06:27.820" end="00:06:29.820" tts:direction="ltr">It starts to become really hard.</p>
        <p begin="00:06:29.820" end="00:06:31.940" tts:direction="ltr">It actually takes a lot of</p>
        <p begin="00:06:31.940" end="00:06:36.840" tts:direction="ltr">brainpower to look at and see how many
